    "title": "Walk-in Drive Logistics Manager at DTDC",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at DTDC. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Logistics Manager to strengthen our Faridabad-based team.\n\nAbout DTDC:\nDTDC is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DTDC!",
